  ${
    $d w x y A $.
    subbas2.1 $e |- B =
           { x | E. y ( y C_ A /\ y e. Fin /\ x = |^| y ) } $.
    $( The collection of finite intersections of any set (subbasis) ` A ` is a
       basis for a topology on ` U. A ` .  Justifies the definition of subbasis
       in [Munkres] p. 82 (after using ~ unitg ). $)
    subbas2 $p |- U. B = U. A $=
      ( vw cuni cv wss cfn wcel cint wceq w3a wex wa cvv vex eleq1 sylibr simpr
